Reasoning: The paper discusses the application of management principles to the software engineering methodology of Extreme Programming (XP), which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the discipline of systems engineering, which is related to software development (cs.SD). The use of moderation techniques and guidelines for scaling up XP suggest a focus on programming languages (cs.PL) and computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the mention of large-scale projects in the telecommunication industry and IT technology consultancy firms suggests a potential focus on cybersecurity (cs.CY).
